column2: "Welcome back, everyone. I'm glad to see none of you were injured."
"Miss Aina... Are you okay?"
"Oh, uh, me? Yeah, I'm... I'm alright."
"Hesitation is a very dangerous thing. Not only for yourself, but also for your allies."
"Gaining control over your emotions is a mental battle that only you can fight."
"R-Right..."
"So, how did the mission go?"
"I must say, your results exceeded even my own expectations."
"I'd like you to continue lending your aid against the DOLLS in much the same fashion."
"Well, for the time being, I have nothing more to ask of you."
"Until your next mission, you're free to do as you please."
"I would suggest honing your skills in one of the Cocoons; explore the world outside of the City."
"In Central City, we also have battle instructors for all classes."
"You would do well to ask them for advice."
"Understood."
"By the way, about fighting Dark Falz. How are the preparations coming along?"
"At the present rate, I should think that we'll be calling on you for your help before long."
"Alright, so just wait until then?"
"Right."
"Finally, take this."
"What's this?"
"It contains written documents about this world, as well as the war with the DOLLS."
"...I see, it sounds useful."
"It's not exactly very organized, though."
"Thanks. I'll make good use of it."
"Good. If it has anything you think might be important, I'd like you to inform me."
"Right. I'll try to be thorough."
